    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This very basic summoning technique conjures a bladed weapon, which rises from the ground at a location within range. The weapon functions like normal, but disappears when the duration runs out or when the duration runs out. The weapon you choose to summon determines the Cost (see table top right). You may double the cost to increase the weapon's size by one size category.<br><br>You may increase the Perform Requirements by 10 to omit the expendable components.<br><br>| Weapon        |   Cost | Weapon           |   Cost |<br>|---------------|--------|------------------|--------|<br>| Battle Wire   |      2 | Kunai            |      1 |<br>| Battleaxe     |      2 | Kunai, curved    |      1 |<br>| Chisa-gatana  |      1 | Kusari-gama      |      3 |<br>| Daigama       |      2 | Naginata         |      2 |<br>| Daikunai      |      2 | Longsword        |      2 |<br>| Dagger        |      1 | Ninja-to         |      2 |<br>| Double Katana |      3 | Nunchaku         |      1 |<br>| Fullblade     |      4 | Quarterstaff     |      3 |<br>| Greatsword    |      3 | Scythe           |      4 |<br>| Hansori       |      2 | Shortsword       |      1 |<br>| Kama          |      1 | Spear            |      3 |<br>| Katana        |      2 | Sabre            |      2 |<br>| Katana, Large |      3 | Spiked Greatmace |      3 |<br>| Knuckle Blade |      1 | Tessen           |      1 |<br>| Kodachi       |      1 | Wakizashi        |      1 |</p>\n\n\n\n",
